name: Lighten up after the dark V2

metadata.name: Gypsophila - Lighten up after the dark
metadata.description:
The smallest flowers in a bouquet of flowers are very often the white gypsophila, because it combines well with other flowers. Gypsophila has many small flowers on a branch. Photographed in close up you can clearly see how beautiful the flowers are. The flowers symbolize eternal love.

For the Lighten up after the dark collection I have up lighted the nature photos, giving them a different twist. They light up from the dark. A beautiful neon effect.
